{
  "stem": "8775.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And I graduated, again with honors, in 1949 after eight years of schooling from the gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And at that time, I decided I wanted to go to university.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And after one year hiatus, I enrolled in 1950 to the Karl Marx University of Economic Sciences, where I wanted to be a certified economist.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And that's what I did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I graduated in 1954 from that university, again, with honors.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very difficult.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My strength actually came from my first cousin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this first cousin was, as I mentioned to you, a lawyer.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "His name was Dr.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Farkas, F-A-R-K-A-S, Shandor, Sandor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he himself survived the forced labor battalions.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he came back and he showed up in 1945.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he took me aside and started talking to me and said, you know, this is how life is.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This is what happens.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It's a terrible thing what happened, but life must go on.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And he tried to live his life.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "As well, he had a girlfriend and he lost his girlfriend as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And from that point on, my cousin, and I was very proud of him, became the prosecutor in Szolnok of the war crimes.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And as a matter of fact, he became quite controversial among Jewish circles, because he prosecuted a fairly prominent Jewish doctor, medical doctor, who was supposedly in Vienna, but he didn't take care of the inmates, of the Jewish people, but he just had his own family put on a higher pedestal.",
      "word_count": 52
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I don't know what other things he was accused of, but this was one of the cases he tried, my first cousin tried.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
